(68087, 200467, 6208, 1, '太陽月亮', '大提琴：張立青 / 小提琴：張譽耀 / 吉他：David Chen / 口簧琴：盧皆興 / 手鼓：魏金寶\n\n阿美族的神話說：太陽是女的 月亮是男的\n太陽眷戀著月亮  月亮依戀著太陽\n太陽忙碌地滋養著大地  月亮則溫暖守候著部落\n太陽月亮相依偎\n\nAccording to the legends of the Pangcah people (which is what the Amis people of Hualien call themselves), the sun is female and the moon is male. The sun loves the moon and the moon is enamored with the sun. The sun busily nourishes the earth, while the moon watches over the village. They rely upon one another in a way that is indicative of how the Pangcah view men and women. I wrote this love song bearing in mind the words of our elders: “Your actions should resemble the sun, while your feelings should be like the moon, if you are to spend a lifetime together.”\n', '2012-05-29 00:00:00', 2012, 25, 0, 17, 'paayaway ko fudal to cidal\nhanhan sato cidal to fudal\nmahanay ko sowa  no matoasy\nO tinako no pangcah\n\nYo’tid sato cidal i palapalaan\nO pinagaan no pangcah a fafahiyan\nO mipaayaway ko fudal to cidal\nO pinagaan no pangcah a fafahiyan\n\nO tinako no matoasay koninan\nMipasifanay i kitanan\nLecad’en o fulad ko faloco’\nlecad’en o cidal ko lakat\nKasasipadung a tatosa （tangasa i toas）\n\n月亮守候著太陽\n太陽眷戀著月亮\n老人家是這樣說的\n這就是阿美族祖先留下來的說法\n\n當太陽溫暖的光 滋養大地\n這就像是我們阿美族的女性一樣\n月亮守候在太陽的背後沉靜\n這就是我們阿美族的男性一樣\n\n老人家訴說著這樣美麗的神話\n並且深深地告訴我們\n心要像月亮\n行走要像太陽\n兩者要互相依伴 （才是永遠）\n', '', 365, '', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '', '風潮音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-11-20 12:51:02', '2015-03-12 14:02:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68088, 200467, 6208, 2, '逝落', '合聲編寫：于立成、胡德夫 / 合聲：胡德夫、于立成、阿洛˙卡力亭˙巴奇辣/ 貝斯：路達瑪幹 / 爵士鼓：魏金寶 / 吉它：柯曉明 / 小提琴：張譽耀\n\n有一年回到部落參加祭典\n遠遠地聽到祭典場上\n族人的歌聲 腳上頓地的鈴鐺聲\n迎著頓地鈴聲的節拍  我幾乎感動得落淚\n\n當我們孩子不再講族語的時候  \n是連山跟海都會難過的事\n回來吧孩子 跟著頓地的節拍\n只要太平洋不斷地拍打著海岸\n我們歌 就要一直唱下去\n\nOne year when I returned to my village to participate in the annual Ocean Rites, I could hear the sound of the festival from far off in the distance. It was the sound of our people singing and of the rhythmic bells attached to their legs. I was moved almost to tears by this, the most beautiful of all our sounds. How much we have lost! Even the mountains and the sea are saddened by the fact that our children cannot speak their mother tongue. Long gone, too, are the mountains where we hunted and the rivers where we fished. Come back, children, come join in the dance! As long as the waves break rhythmically on the shore, we must continue to sing our songs.\n', '2012-05-29 00:00:00', 2012, 25, 0, 17, ' o ngiha no pangcah a tamdaw o pasifana no matoasay\n ladatwsan ladatwsan\n o sowal ita o halateng ita a orip\n away to away to\n\n ya kamifutingan ta itiya ho a alo\n ya kamiadopan ta a lotok\n ya kamicekiwan ta itiya ho a liyal\n tayla cowa tu \n\nO wa iye yan o wa o wa yan\nO wa o wa o wa owa iye o way yan\nO wa iye yan o wa o wa yan\nO wa o wa o wa owa iye o way yan\n\n 阿美族從祖先學到的知識\n 消失了 消失了\n 阿美族自祖先呼喚的生命\n 逝去了 逝去了\n\n 那個曾經補過魚的溪流\n 那個曾經獵狩的山巒\n 那個曾經採集貝類的海洋\n 到底去了哪裡\n\n（虛詞）\n', '', 342, '', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '', '風潮音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-11-20 12:51:34', '2015-03-12 14:02:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68089, 200467, 6208, 3, '身體', '合聲：撒布爾．嘎照、依佑．嘎照 / 烏克麗麗：David Chen  / 金貝鼓：魏金寶 / 沙鈴：魏金寶 / 口哨：施嘯天\n\n在祭典場上\n我們的身體過去是迎著祖先來的方位虔敬\n但現在我們  卻是取悅背後的觀光客\n身體應該朝向祖先來的方向\n身體應該舞著海的律動\n我們不該迷失在鎂光燈與遊客之間\n\nIn the past, at the yearly festival, we would respectfully turn ourselves toward the direction from which our ancestors came. But today we try to please the tourists who watch us from behind. We should face our ancestors and dance to the rhythm of the ocean. We must not lose ourselves in a sea of lights and tourists.\n', '2012-05-29 00:00:00', 2012, 25, 0, 17, 'kafana’ an ko tiring nala ccay  i ‘olah\nosifana’ no toasta ta ti’eren no mita\nmatiyal o riyar awa’ay ko patolasan\no tangal no toas matiyal o tokos\n\no wa hay yan  o wa hay yan\no tayla cowa’ay ko Ilisin tayra i da’oc\ntiring no mako matipotay no niaro’ kita\ntiring no mako raromadiw to saki niaro’ kita\n\n孩子們在祭典場上的身體 是從延續的愛而來\n是來自祖先叮嚀與訓示\n就像大海般的深邃遼遠不可測\n而老人的智慧 就像雋永的高山一樣\n\no wa hay yan  o wa hay yan\n祭典就是如此能夠延續到永遠\n我們的身體 就是如此被部落深深的守護著\n我們的身體 就是要如此歌唱一直到永遠\n', '', 198, '', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '', '風潮音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-11-20 12:51:50', '2015-03-12 14:02:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68090, 200467, 6208, 4, '我不知道我是想念海還是想念你', '鋼琴：張聖潔\n\n有天我走沿著海岸走著\n突然發現高樓四起 遊客變多 民宿興盛\n曾經孰悉的海 突然變了顏色\n看著海 我心裡想著\n海 是我們打獵的地方、虔敬的對象\n海 是孕育我們部落的奶水、孩子遊戲的家\n但這一切都被阻擋了  有一種失落\n我不知道是想念海 還是想念你\n這句話是說 多年之後 \n我們還會不會認識祖先走過的那片海\n\nOne day while walking along the seashore, I found myself surrounded by buildings, guest houses and tourists. The once familiar ocean had changed colors. I felt lost as I looked at the distant sea, the place where the Pangcah people fish and hold their Ocean Rites, the water which enriched our village, the place where our children play, gradually being blocked from view. I composed this song, in the fear that years from now I will no longer recognize this place where our ancestors once walked. \n', '2012-05-29 00:00:00', 2012, 25, 0, 17, 'hay yan  hay yan  hay yan  o way yan\nhay yan  o way yan  hay yan  oway yan\nhay yan o way yan  hoi yo ho hay yan  hay yan\nhay yan o way yan  hoi yo ho hay yan  hay yan  o way yan\nhay yan o way yan\nhay yan o way yan\n\n（口白）\nMaaraw to no mako kiso\nParatoh ko fali to kasaccay no miso\nIra:ay kako a minengneng i kisoan\nNa i tolon no riyar alsin\nOya falatfatay ko tdi no miso\nNai kasasiarawan no mita\nLipahak a comikay i tafoktafokan\nCaayho ka palita` ako kiso\n\nSaicel sa kiso a misiayaw to pades\nO maan ko i falo`coay a demak iso?\nCaay ka fana` koya maeferay ayam\nTayni kako a mingenng i kisoan\nKafokilan ko piharateng  to riyar hato ikisoan\n\n\n(虛詞)\n終於 我來看你了 \n風說 你一直很孤獨  \n我遠遠的看著你 \n在曾經海祭的禱告中\n你曾如此波光閃爍的光芒  \n在我們曾經相識的日子\n徜徉快樂奔跑在沙灘上\n我其實看不穿你 \n\n你總是傲然地迎著滄桑與破壞 \n甚麼是妳的祕密心事呢\n海鷗他 也不明白 \n終於 我來看你了 \n我不知道 我是想念海 還是想念你\n', '', 398, '', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '', '風潮音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-11-20 12:52:28', '2015-03-12 14:02:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68091, 200467, 6208, 5, '馬太鞍', '編曲：劉詩偉 / 合聲：阿洛˙卡力亭˙巴奇辣、拉藍˙阿帕克、宋曉玲、林晶瀅、曾明吉、林欣宜、余正雄、曾添義、張智晨、張勇雄\n\n馬太鞍是我故鄉  來自母親的家鄉\n遠遠山腳下的家鄉  是我的依歸\n無論遇到任何困境都能支持我、安慰我\n帶給我堅強的力量   隨時撫慰我的傷痛\n這首歌獻給部落 以及每年祭典上認真維繫的年齡階級\n獻給我的階級拉可林  \n重要的是  獻給我的母親\n\nFata’an is the name of my village, the place from which my mother came. This village, nestled at the base of a distant mountain, has become a refuge for me, a source of support when I’m working far away in the big city. No matter what hardships I encounter, the village consoles me and gives me energy. It heals my wounds. This song is for my village and for all of the people of Lakelin, the age-grade to which I belong within our traditional tribal structure. Most of all, it is for my mother.\n', '2012-05-29 00:00:00', 2012, 25, 0, 17, 'I ayaw sara no lotok\nMaaraw rako falo \nFalo mala huci kaka’en ho rairai\nI ayaw sara no lotok\nMisaloma’ ko matoasay\nI nian sani o Fata’an\n\nNa no ayaw ko ya dai to dofot\nMalikoda ko wawa\nLipahakay kitaa widang\nKona ni Fata’anay\n\nO Fata’an fangcalay a niaro’\nMakapahay a awi  Marolay kita kasa saan\nO Fata’an o pasifana’ ni Unak Tafon\nMapakahay a niaro’\n\n很多年前在遙遠的山腳下\n祖先看到了一片黃金花海\n花海結成了果子 餵養族人世代\n在很多年以前 在遙遠的山腳下\n祖先建立的家園\n這就是我的部落馬太鞍\n\n很多年以後 我們背起情人袋\n年輕人正唱著歌 跳著舞\n在祭典場上 我們是驕傲的階級\n因為我們來自馬太鞍\n\n馬太鞍 是美麗的故鄉\n優秀的年齡階級  是我們累了要休息的地方\n馬太鞍 是部落老頭目Unak Tafon的諄諄教誨\n美麗的部落\n', '', 192, '', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '', '風潮音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-11-20 12:52:46', '2015-03-12 14:02:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68092, 200467, 6208, 6, '喔喔歌', '合聲編寫：阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣 / 合聲：阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣 / 吉它：David Chen \n\n歌詞大意：\n孩子 我的孩子 好好睡吧！\n不要擔心 不要害怕 我來唱歌給你聽\n太陽下山 月亮探頭\n河邊的青蛙都來唱歌給你聽\n樹上的貓頭鷹守候著你\n孩子 我的孩子 好好睡吧！\n晚安 晚安了\n\nThis song is composed exclusively of function words, which are used in singing. It can be roughly translated as such:  “Child, my child, sleep well./ Do not worry, do not be afraid/ I’ve come to sing you a song./ The sun has come down from the mountains./ The moon has lifted up his head./ The frogs by the riverside/ Have come to sing for you./ The owl in the tree/ Watches over you. / Child, my child, sleep well. / Good night, my child, good night.”\n', '2012-05-29 00:00:00', 2012, 25, 0, 17, 'o o o o hay yan\no o o o hay yan\no o o o hay yan\no o o o hay yan\n\nhay yan hay yan\niyeng iyeng hay yan\nhay yan o\niyeng iyeng hay yan\n\n（虛詞）', '', 254, '', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '', '風潮音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-11-20 12:53:10', '2015-03-12 14:02:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68093, 200467, 6208, 7, '肩膀', '編曲：于立成 / 合聲編寫：于立成 / 合聲：于立成 / RAP: Lee Way（英文詞）、于立成（說）\n\n老人家常說 我們要有肩膀\n肩膀就是意味著 人就是要有責任 要有擔當\n我們才能有態度面對生命的試煉\n祭典中 我們最常聽到這樣的訓示與叮嚀\n階級的訓練 就是要迎著祖先的肩膀\n共同扛起部落的責任\n\nOur elders often say that we must “have shoulders.” In other words, we must be able to shoulder responsibility in order to face the challenges that life presents. The training offered at each age-grade level enables our people to shoulder the village responsibilities, which have been passed down through the generations.\n', '2012-05-29 00:00:00', 2012, 25, 0, 17, 'kalo slal ira ko sowal no kapah\no masowalay a kimad ira ko tayal\nadihay ko tayal adihay ko kafukilan (rap1)\nadihay ko pilife’t ta mala fainayan (rap2)\n\nci afala’ ko kapah mafana to lalan\nci afala ko kapah to mafana’ to tiring\nkapahaw o kalo pilifet no mita\no sapipalowad to niyaro’\n(rap3)\n\nRAP1：Ride with me girl....to this beat y''all. Ain''t nothin'' in the world... Stoppin'' me hopeful \nRAP2：I never thought soulful could be this simple. Take a flight with me yea! nothin'' eva stops... mah flow \nRAP3：When the beat, beat, drops I feel so hot. So hot reminds me never eva give up  \nStay cool cheers to everyone at the next spot. Cuz u know I ain''t ever gonna quit and stop.  \nI never thought life should be allowed to go bad. Snap of a finger man and another life goes wack?! \n      but it''s all good, yea I stay true to the word that proves positivity survives all odds!  \n\n\n每一個階級 每一個訓示\n每一個被交付的責任\n他是經歷無數徬徨的試煉\n他是經過拉扯與蹂躪而成為真正的男人\n\n年輕人的肩膀阿 你明白我們的道路嗎\n年輕人的肩膀阿 你知道自己是誰嗎\n年輕人的肩膀阿  我們每次經歷的拉扯\n就是扛起部落的責任\n', '', 296, '', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '', '風潮音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-11-20 12:53:36', '2015-03-12 14:02:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68094, 200467, 6208, 8, '聖山', '合聲：撒布爾˙嘎照、依佑˙嘎照 / 鋼琴：張聖潔 / 大提琴：張立青\n\n部落的阿公生前常常指著山頭說\n這是孕育我們祖先的聖山叫cilangasan\n我們遵照阿公的話走上山去\n阿公有交代\n不要沿著海邊走 要向著太陽下山的方向走\n因為這是老人家走過的路\n後來寫這首歌我才知道\n阿公的故事不只用「講的」\n阿公希望年輕人用「走的」方式去知道\n\nBefore he passed away, one of the old men from our village would often point to a nearby mountain and say: “That is Cilangasan, the holy mountain from which our ancestors came.” We followed his instructions, preparing necessities like salt and rice, and we climbed the mountain walking in the direction of the setting sun. I climbed Cilangasan three times, but it wasn’t until I wrote a song about it that I realized that the elder wanted us to tell his story not just with words but with our footsteps.\n', '2012-05-29 00:00:00', 2012, 25, 0, 17, 'Ira ko ccay a lotok\nO cidal o orip cingra\nO pahecla''an no tatoasan a pala itila cingra\n\nCilangasan o ina\nCilangasan o cidal\nCilangasan o orip\nKa alosa itini no liyal \n（Paayaway to cidal no cilangasan）\n\nmahan pineng no mita ko rolay no tatoasan\nterey sa kita a minengneng no narolay ko sral ita\nyo mo raraw ko rakat no tatoasan\nmitolo to lotok ko wawa no mita\ntangec ko cilangsan\nfute''sa ko mata no cilangasan\nto mangec ko cilagasan\nfute'' sa ko mata no cilangasan\n\n\n有一座山\n是太陽   是生命\n她是我們祖先來的地方\n\n她是我們的母親\n她是太陽照的地方\n她是生命\n沉靜地座落在海的旁邊\n迎著陽光照射的地方就是妳 cilangasan\n\n這是多少祖先們  曾經一同走過的路\n現在我們卻只是遙遠地 安靜地看著這座山\n不再走向祖先走過的步伐\n我們孩子 已不再仰望著山\n我們的山 她在哭泣\n我們的山 她難過地閉上了雙眼\n我們的山 難過地不再說話\n我們的山 難過地不想再睜開雙眼\n', '', 334, '', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '', '風潮音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-11-20 12:54:06', '2015-03-12 14:02:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68095, 200467, 6208, 9, '回家的饗宴', '編曲：康愷哲 / 合聲：阿洛˙卡力亭˙巴奇辣、路達瑪幹、拉藍˙阿帕克、宋曉玲、林晶瀅、曾明吉、林欣宜、余正雄、曾添義、張智晨、張勇雄\n\n常常會問旅外唸書或工作的阿美族朋說\n「你看到什麼東西就會想家」\n大部份的人會回答「我看到tatoken就會想哭」\n只要部落媽媽宅急便來的菜\n就是我們寒風凜冽時 最重要的依靠\n\n吃 對阿美族來說就像回到家 \n是溫暖的步驟\n各種野菜佳餚 家人朋友就會聚上好幾回\n即使在外有多麼不好 有多麼不舒服\n回家   一切就有了答案\n\n“What makes you homesick?” This is something I often ask my Pangcah friends who are working or studying far away from home. Most of them say, “When I see tatoken (an indigenous leafy green) it moves me to tears.” Our mothers often send us express deliveries of traditional fare, the perfect comfort food when the weather turns cold. For the Pangcah, it is these foods – more than money or a beautiful house – which embody the meaning of “home.”\n', '2012-05-29 00:00:00', 2012, 25, 0, 17, 'Maharateng ko loma’ ma’an kiso maharateng ko kakae’nen\nMaruray’ay kiso sakama’an maharateng ko kakae’nen\nCcay a kiso sakama’an maharateng ko kakae’nen\nIra ko idang kiso sakama’an maharateng ko kakae’nen\n\nSiraw  ke’naw  cumuli  tatukem\nHakhak  torem  cekiw  facidol\nKakorot  lokot  dognc  kolasain\nCamol to epah\n\nAy cha! Matefad  ko losa’ lipahak ko faloco’\nMapolong a asalikaka makero ato romadiw\nPacocoay paoripay mitosay ko rateng\nAno milaliw kita to loma’ tayra i maci\nMaherateng ko iloma’ay a rateng\nItini itapak matayal salikaka\nSani opitiuran no faloco’\n\n\n想家的時候 我會想吃甚麼\n很疲憊的時候 我們會想吃甚麼\n心裡很孤單的時候 我們會想吃甚麼\n見到好朋友的時候  我們會想吃甚麼\n\n醃豬肉 蔥 蝸牛 大頭根\n糯米飯 麻糬 貝螺 麵包果\n苦瓜 山蘇 黃藤心 花生\n配上一杯酒\n\n哎呀! 只要吃一口 我們的眼淚就會掉下來 心理安慰\n大家也會圍過來 聚在一起唱歌跳舞\n這些菜是孕育我們奶水 餵養我們長大的力量我們到現在才知道\n即使長大了 離開家到了都市\n我們都會常常想念這些菜\n', '', 210, '', '楊慕仁', '阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣', '', '風潮音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-11-20 12:54:23', '2015-03-12 14:02:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68096, 200467, 6208, 10, '送靈歌', '編曲：阿洛．卡力亭．巴奇辣 / 合聲: 撒布爾．嘎照、依佑．嘎照 / 貝斯：路達瑪幹 / 爵士鼓 魏金寶 / 吉它：柯曉明\n\n歌詞大意：\n這是傳統的祭典歌謠\n在祭典的最後一天  我們稱為送靈\n送靈的那天 全部落族人都會落淚  \n因為我們知道  祖先的靈是滿足的\n在我們滿載的歌聲中 豐收的稻米 \n婦女孩子的笑聲中 渡過平安的一年\n\nThis song has no lyrics; it is a traditional melody sung on the last day of the festival when the village sees off the ancestral spirits. On that day, everyone in the village is moved to tears because they know that the ancestral spirits are content. We lift up our voices in song to rejoice in a plentiful rice harvest, and the laughter of the women and girls of the village marks the passing of yet another peaceful year.\n', '2012-05-29 00:00:00', 2012, 25, 0, 17, '[領唱] o hey ya o hai yan \n[答唱] Hey ya o ho wa hai yan \n[領唱] Hay ya o wa hai ye \n[答唱] Hey ya o ho wa hai yan \n\n（虛詞）\n', '', 268, '', '阿美族豐濱鄉豐年祭典歌謠 ', '阿美族豐濱鄉豐年祭典歌謠 ', '', '風潮音樂', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-11-20 12:54:49', '2015-03-12 14:02:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68097, 93181, 0, 1, 'Endless Fight（測試版）', '每天的營營役役，每天的燈紅酒綠，我的信心已經不復往昔，究竟我是為了什麼而選擇一次又一次的踏上那熟悉的舞台？我只能在那永不停歇的時間長河中隨波逐流了嗎？\n\n有一天我剛出了車禍，驚魂甫定的我為了一個想法深深嘆息：「現在的我生命若結束了，無論我做過什麼事情，我也跟所有人一樣，沉到河底，大體重重堆疊，迎接下一場氾濫；若有幸將來百年歸老，無論我做過什麼，結果亦是一樣。\n\n那為什麼還要瞻前顧後、小心翼翼的活著？為了自己而活著，衝上舞台虜獲觀眾的一切，即使我將變得面目全非，我要將他們都變成我的所有物，直至死亡，阿門。', '2014-12-31 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 2, 1, 'Left the stage and had that bitter wine\nShe asked me why bothered going around\nThat night''d already turned the leaves into bills\njust paid her and made that divine\n\nI went to see the master of fame\nHe told me just stood still at the spot\n"Crash, hit and run, speed to dead or reach your destination.\n\nThe steering wheel in your hands is all that matters,\nWho to be the passenger as well."\n\nGouging out your eyes\nCutting off your ears\nMy goal is not to be a saint\nSold my soul\nact as a publicity stunt\n\nRipping off my face\nPosioning my mind\nDon''t tell me how to be a saint\njust to live on\njust to pant even one more moment to live on', '', 211, '', 'Jeff Cho', 'Kalmarr Lam', 'DaNaiPow打奶泡樂團', 'HaiNuoYa海諾亞', '', 0, 1, 1, '2013-11-20 13:18:29', '2014-05-22 09:31:42', '2014-05-22 09:31:42'),
